overview.longBusinessSummary: European Wax Center, Inc. operates as the franchisor and operator of out-of-home waxing services in the United States. It offers body and facial waxing services; and pre- and post-service products, including ingrown hair serums, exfoliating gels, brow shapers, and skin treatments, as well as skincare retail products. European Wax Center, Inc. was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Plano, Texas.
